  <brief_title>Do we Prepare Patients for Their Digital Legacy? A Survey of Palliative Care Professionals in the West Midlands</brief_title>
  <official_title>Do we Prepare Patients for Their Digital Legacy? A Survey of Palliative Care Professionals in the West Midlands</official_title>
