  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Conduct a questionnaire survey of palliative care professionals including doctors, nurses and
      social workers currently working within the West Midlands to establish how much the
      palliative care community in the West Midlands engage in preparing patients for their digital
      legacy and find out if there is a further education need in this community about digital
      legacy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
